# My Notebook - Flask Notes App

A simple notes application built using Python, Flask, and SQLite.

## Live Demo
https://digital-notes-app-2iua.onrender.com

> Note: The first load may take 30–50 seconds because it is hosted on Render's free plan.

## Tech Stack
- Python
- Flask
- SQLite
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript
- Render

## Features
- Create, Read, Update, and Delete notes
- REST API
- Real-time search
- Dark/Light theme
- Live deployment on Render

## Run Locally

```bash
git clone https://github.com/JyothiPeddireddy/Digital_Notes_App.git
cd Digital_Notes_App
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```

## Current Limitation
- Uses SQLite, so data may reset when the free hosting server restarts.

## Future Improvements
- Migrate to PostgreSQL
- Add user authentication
- Add note categories
